In re Resignation of Sanders.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Sanders (1995), 73 Ohio St.3d 1209.]

(No. 95-1395 Submitted July 26, 1995 Decided July 27, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of Daniel Joseph Sanders of Toledo, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0008953, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
